nkedIn%20because%20I%20was%20doing%20a%20professional%20reset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetworking-important-new-job-economy-ai-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enetwork%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20even%20reached%20out%20to%20my%20girlfriend's%20dad's%20cousin's%20husband%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20a%20company%20I%20was%20interested%20in.%20I%20did%20an%20informational%20interview%20with%20him%2C%20and%20he%20offered%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20people%20at%20his%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20time%20I'd%20done%20about%20100%20applications%2C%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20this%20is%20actually%20a%20lot%20more%20difficult%20than%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20536%20days%20and%20688%20applications%2C%20but%20I'm%20glad%20to%20say%20I%20finally%20made%20it%20and%20got%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220b10dfba-cb4a-4c7d-9264-5bcc4116e624%5C%22%3ECompletely%20blindsided%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20always%20easy.%20I%20had%20236%20rejections%20and%20didn't%20get%20a%20response%20or%20got%20ghosted%20on%20449%20of%20the%20applications.%20I%20had%2015%20screening%20calls%20with%20HR%20and%2018%20referrals%20for%20various%20jobs.%20I%20think%20one%20or%20two%20of%20those%20referrals%20got%20me%20to%20a%20screening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20application%20594%2C%20I%20got%20an%20offer.%20It%20was%20for%20a%20company%20here%20in%20Southern%20California%20to%20be%20a%20quality-assurance%20technician.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20first%20interview%2C%20they%20said%20they%20wanted%20to%20hire%20me.%20I%20had%20to%20do%20some%20paperwork%20and%20a%20drug%20test.%20I%20got%20a%20call%20back%20saying%20the%20drug%20test%20was%20good%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20give%20them%20my%20Social%20Security%20card.%20I%20suggested%20starting%20a%20week%20and%20a%20half%20later.%20A%20representative%20from%20the%20company%20said%20they%20would%20talk%20to%20the%20hi