%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fsilicon-valley-would-become-stupid-valley-maga-activist-schooled-for-demanding-reservation-for-us-citizens-in-tech-jobs%2Famp_articleshow%2F121888506.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20TikTok-famous%20spin%20scrubber%20is%20my%20favorite%20cleaning%20hack%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20watching%20the%20grime%20dissolve%20away%20is%20so%20satisfying%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20with%20pink%20fingernails%20uses%20the%20Casabella%20Power%20Scrubber%20on%20a%20sunroom%20window.%20The%20backyard%20is%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684b33a185e81483682c00b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI'd%20had%20enough%20with%20endless%20scrubbing%20for%20mediocre%20results%2C%20so%20I%20turned%20to%20the%20Casabella%20Power%20Spin%20Scrubber.%20Months%20later%2C%20I'm%20so%20glad%20I%20did.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20moved%20into%20my%20rental%20house%2C%20it%20became%20abundantly%20clear%20that%20my%20landlord%20and%20I%20have%20different%20definitions%20of%20%26quot%3Bprofessionally%20clean.%26quot%3B%20After%20driving%20the%2010%20hour%20trek%20to%20Indiana%20from%20Kansas%20with%20all%20of%20my%20things%20in%20tow%2C%20I%20was%20dismayed%20when%20I%20was%20greeted%20by%20filthy%20grout%2C%20crayon%20on%20the%20walls%2C%20and%20caked%20on%20soap%20scum%20in%20the%20bathrooms.%20In%20that%20moment%2C%20I%20could%20see%20my%20future%2C%20and%20it%20contained%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20on%20my%20hands%20and%20knees%20scrubbing%20up%20other%20people's%20messes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20after%20seeing%20electric%20spin%20scrubbers%20all%20over%20TikTok%20and%20reading%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-electric-spin-scrubber%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20electric%20spin%20scrubber%20guide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20was%20intrigued.%20These%20tools%20seemed%20like%20magic%2C%20making%20dirt%20and%20grime%20disappear%20with%20the%20touch%20of%20a%20button%E2%80%94%20no%20arduous%20scrubbing%20required.%20I%20finally%20decided%20to%20spend%20the%20%2450%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Da9b747fc2663117f9214a852e00f1ec53522994db6c20018746826600f6ae440%26postID%3D684b2fb914270c4174af9708%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fcasabella-power-spin-scrubber-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FCasabella-Power-Spin-Scrubber-Extendable%252Fdp%252FB0D42BSWDN%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECasabella%20Power%20Spin%20Scrubber%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20months%20later%2C%20I%20am%20so%20glad%20that%20I%20did.%20It's%20saved%20me%20time%20cleaning%20every%20room%20in%20my%20house%2C%20and%20it's%20able%20to%20reach%20a%20level%20of%20clean%20I%20could%20never%20achieve%20with%20a%20bucket%20and%20a%20mop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227c764b43-cc54-476d-ae89-351ba72967f5%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20review%20of%20the%20Casabella%20Power%20Spin%20Scrubber%5C%22%3EThe%20power%20spin%20scrubber%20is%20lightweight%2C%20versatile%2C%20and%20powerful%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224027%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20fully%20extended%20Casabella%20spin%20scrubber%20on%20a%20blue%20and%20green%20rug.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684b35f385e81483682c0126%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222014%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFully%20extended%2C%20the%20spin%20scrubber%20is%2047.5%20inches%20long.%20It's%20a%20good%20height%20for%20cleaning%20floors%20or%20hard-to-reach%20places.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWeighing%20just%203.57%20pounds%2C%20the%20Casabella%20Power%20Spin%20Scubber%20is%20light%20and%20portable.%20It's%20cordless%2C%20too%2C%20so%20you%20won't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20having%20enough%20cord%20length%20as%20you%20clean.%20With%20just%20one%20ultra-powerful%20speed%2C%20it%20turns%20on%20and%20off%20when%20you%20press%20a%20button.%20There's%20no%20need%20to%20cycle%20through%20speeds%20or%20modes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20battery%20lasts%20100%20minutes.%20I've%20never%20had%20problems%20with%20it%20dying%20during%20my%20usual%20cleaning%20routine%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20bathrooms%2C%20kitchen%2C%20and%20floors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spin%20scrubber%20comes%20with%20four%20brush%20heads%3A%20a%20small%20flat%20brush%20for%20detail%20work%2C%20a%20large%20flat%20brush%20for%20large%20areas%2C%20an%20angled%20brush%20for%20hard-to-reach%20places%2C%20and%20a%20dome%20brush%20for%20curved%20spaces%20like%20sinks%20and%20tubs.%20Each%20brush%20head%20attaches%20easily%20to%20the%20scrubber%20body%2C%20although%20it%20does%20take%20some%20force%20to%20detach%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20how%20the%20scrubber%20is%20fully%20adjustable.%20The%20cleaning%20head%20pivots%20at%2045%20and%2090%20degrees%20to%20give%20me%20the%20right%20leverage%20at%20the%20right%20angle%2C%20while%20the%20handle%20extends%20from%2027%20inches%20up%20to%2047.5%20inches.%20This%20adjustability%20means%20that%20you%20won't%20have%20to%20bend%20over%20or%20even%20get%20on%20your%20knees%20to%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20turn%20it%20on%2C%20you'll%20notice%20that%20the%20speed%20is%20very%20fast.%20While%20this%20is%20great%20for%20scrubbing%20power%2C%20it%20also%20means%20that%20the%20spin%20scrubber%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20control.%20If%20you%20don't%20apply%20enough%20pressure%2C%20it%20will%20fly%20off%20whatever%20you're%20cleaning.%20It's%20certainly%20a%20step%20up%20from%20manually%20scrubbing%20and%20cleaning%2C%20but%20it%20still%20takes%20a%20bit%20of%20effort%20to%20keep%20it%20under%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2249e0d16f-0963-449f-8bd5-37648601fb98%5C%22%3EIt%20has%20transformed%20how%20I%20clean%20my%20bathroom%2C%20cutting%20cleaning%20time%20in%20half.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20with%20pink%20nails%20holds%20the%20Casabella%20Power%20Scrubber%20as%20it%20cleans%20a%20tiled%20bathroom%20wall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684b3703f748d8c055f39ad0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20I%20moved%2C%20the%20bathroom%20was%20one%20of%20the%20dirtiest%20places%20in%20the%20rental%20house.%20The%20spin%20scrubber%20actually%20helps%20me%20feel%20clean.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20my%20Casabella%20Power%20Spin%20Scrubber%20mostly%20to%20use%20in%20my%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20blown%20away%20by%20its%20performance.%20One%20of%20my%20most%20hated%20chores%20is%20cleaning%20the%20shower%20and%20bathtub%3B%20it's%20so%20hard%20to%20scrub%20away%20soap%20scum%20and%20hard%20water%20stains.%20My%20shower%20is%20tiled%2C%20so%20hard%20water%20tends%20to%20build%20up%20in%20the%20grout%2C%20making%20it%20ridiculously%20difficult%20to%20get%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20house%20I'm%20renting%20is%2C%20to%20put%20it%20kindly%2C%20well-loved.%20With%20its%20chipping%20paint%2C%20my%20bathtub%20is%20particularly%20rundown%2C%20so%20it's%20hard%20for%20me%20to%20feel%20like%20it's%20really%20clean.%20As%20a%20renter%20who%20cares%20about%20cleanliness%2C%20it's%20really%20difficult%20when%20I%20don't%20feel%20clean%20in%20my%20own%20home.%20I%20don't%20like%20knowing%20that%20there's%20dust%20and%20grime%20from%20other%20people%20in%20my%20space%2C%20so%20cleaning%20is%20usually%20a%20laborious%20process.%20I%20deeply%20care%20about%20a%20thorough%20clean%2C%20especially%20in%20my%20bathroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20of%20white%20tile%20walls.%20The%20left%20side%20is%20noticeably%20grimier%20than%20the%20right%20side.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684b380a3d5881a51c1b533d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20only%20a%20minute%20of%20scrubbing%2C%20you%20can%20see%20a%20noticeable%20difference%20between%20my%20bathroom%20tile%20before%20and%20after%20cleaning.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20used%20my%20spin%20scrubber%20in%20my%20shower%2C%20I%20was%20amazed.%20The%20soap%20scum%20was%20removed%20like%20it%20was%20nothing%2C%20and%20the%20orangish-red%20stains%20from%20my%20hard%20water%20disappeared%20quickly.%20The%20different%20brush%20heads%20came%20in%20handy%20here%2C%20too.%20I%20used%20the%20large%20flat%20brush%20on%20the%20walls%20for%20an%20all-over%20clean.%20The%20dome%20brush%20cleaned%20the%20curved%20sides%20of%20my%20bathtub%2C%20and%20the%20angled%20brush%20got%20the%20hard-to-reach%20places%20under%20my%20faucet.%20Once%20I%20was%20done%20cleaning%20my%20shower%2C%20the%20rinsed%20water%20was%20filthy%E2%80%94%20a%20good%20sign%20that%2C%20for%20once%2C%20my%20shower%20was%20actually%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spin%20scrubber%20also%20works%20great%20on%20sinks%20and%20around%20the%20toilet.%20I%20always%20make%20sure%20to%20clean%20the%20brush%20heads%20in%20a%20disinfecting%20concoction%20before%20moving%20between%20surfaces%2C%20though%2C%20so%20I'm%20not%20spreading%20germs%20all%20around%20my%20house.%20On%20cleaning%20days%2C%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20argue%