22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echanges%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20mirror%20what's%20happening%20not%20only%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Fcannes-lions-cmo-insider-breakfast-media-marketing-tech-convergence-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emarketing%3C%2Fa%3E%20industry%2C%20but%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20these%20includes%20expanding%20the%20aperture%20of%20Glass%3A%20The%20Lion%20for%20Change%2C%20which%20celebrates%20creativity%20that%20promotes%20equal%20representation%2C%20beyond%20just%20gender%2C%20to%20include%20disability%2C%20race%2C%20sexuality%2C%20and%20social%20inequity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExpanding%20its%20scope%20allows%20us%20to%20celebrate%20ideas%20promoting%20equitable%20representation%20across%20a%20broader%20range%20of%20communities%2C%20while%20emphasizing%20authentic%20inclusivity%20throughout%20the%20creative%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marian%20Brannelly%2C%20the%20global%20director%20of%20awards%20for%20the%20Lions%2C%20in%20an%20email%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20addition%20is%20subtle%2C%20but%20important%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20growing%20presence%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fb2b-influencers-rise-key-findings-marketing-survey-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EB2B%20campaigns%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20Lions.%20The%20Creative%20B2B%20Lions%20submission%20will%20now%20include%20a%20question%20to%20help%20clarify%20the%20type%20of%20work%20submitted.%20Entrants%20will%20need%20to%20specify%20if%20the%20work%20is%20for%20a%20traditional%20B2B%20model%20where%20one%20business%20sells%20directly%20to%20another%2C%20one%20involving%20a%20partnership%20between%20businesses%20to%20reach%20consumers%2C%20or%20work%20aimed%20at%20attracting%20consumers%20as%20a%20way%20to%20engage%20a%20business%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20the%20jury%20is%20looking%20for%20work%20that%20redefines%20how%20B2B