3Cp%3ESouthwest%20Airlines%20is%20rolling%20out%20advanced%20cockpit%20alert%20systems%20across%20its%20entire%20fleet%20of%20Boeing%20737%20aircraft%20to%20help%20pilots%20avoid%20dangerous%20runway%20mistakes%2C%20including%20wrong-surface%20takeoffs%2C%20high-speed%20landings%2C%20and%20unstable%20approaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20has%20equipped%20more%20than%20700%20aircraft%20with%20SmartRunway%20and%20SmartLanding%20software%20developed%20by%20Honeywell%20Aerospace%20Technologies%2C%20a%20global%20aviation%20technology%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20programs%20work%20by%20providing%20pilots%20with%20real-time%20visual%20and%20audio%20alerts%20during%20taxi%2C%20takeoff%2C%20and%20landing%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BOn%20taxiway%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BToo%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BToo%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BLong%20landing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20systems%20build%20on%20Honeywell's%20Enhanced%20Ground%20Proximity%20Warning%20System%2C%20which%20was%20already%20installed%20on%20Southwest's%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20system%20is%20design%20to%20prevent%20the%20kinds%20of%20potentially%20catastrophic%20errors%20that%20have%20become%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairplane-experts-stumped-by-high-rate-of-near-miss-collisions-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ealarmingly%20frequent%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20US%20airports%2C%20including%20one%20in%20February%20when%20a%20Southwest%20Airlines%20jet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouthwest-near-miss-private-jet-chicago-midway-runway-video-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enarrowly%20avoided%20a%20collision%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20private%20jet%20in%20Chicago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday's%20pilots%20face%20increasing%20challenges%2C%20including%20unpredictable%20weather%20and%20dense%20traffic%20in%20limited%20airspace%2C%20forcing%20them%20to%20make%20split-second%20decisions%20during%20takeoff%20and%20landing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jim%20Currier%2C%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20Honeywell%20Aerospace%20Technologies%2C%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSouthwest%20is%20continuing%20to%20put%20pilots%20and%20passengers%20first%20by%20investing%20in%20SmartRunway%20and%20SmartLanding%20software%20across%20its%20fleet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Honeywell%2C%20the%20technology%20is%20already%20certified%20for%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20Airbus%20and%20Boeing%20aircraft%20and%20is%20already%20in%20use%20by%20several%20carriers%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20its%20availability%2C%20many%20airlines%20have%20chosen%20not%20to%20activate%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAirlines%20elect%20whether%20they%20want%20to%20activate%20this%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20Adam%20Kress%2C%20Honeywell's%20director%20of%20external%20communications%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20available%20for%20years.%20There%20is%20a%20cost%20associated%20with%20it%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20free%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20also%20not%20mandated.%20Some%20select%20it%2C%20some%20don't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoneywell%20and%20Southwest%20did%20not%20share%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKress%20said%20interest%20in%20the%20alert%20system%20has%20grown%20over%20the%20past%20year%20or%20two%2C%20driven%20by%20rising%20air%20traffic%20and%20a%20series%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-air-lines-air-force-involved-near-miss-incident-dc-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehigh-profile%20close%20calls%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20busy%20airports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPublic%20customers%20of%20the%20technology%20include%20Emirates%20and%20Alaska%20Airlines%2C%20but%20many%20airlines%20still%20haven't%20opted%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouthwest%20began%20activating%20the%20system%20in%20early%202024%20as%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20initiative%20to%20manage%20emerging