.%20Based%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20it%20ardently%20advocates%20for%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20rights%20and%20delivers%20comprehensive%20health%20services%2C%20including%20free%20HIV%20testing%20and%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20community-based%20organisation%20also%20champions%20mental%20health%2C%20legal%20advocacy%2C%20and%20workplace%20inclusion%20through%20initiatives%20like%20the%20Saksham%20job%20fair%2C%20a%20community-led%20employment%20drive%20first%20held%20in%20April%202022.%20It%20goes%20beyond%20a%20typical%20job%20fair%2C%20bringing%20together%20panel%20discussions%2C%20upskilling%20workshops%2C%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20reviews%2C%20career%20counselling%2C%20and%20structured%20interviews.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20proactive%20contributions%20ensure%20the%20protection%20and%20promotion%20of%20health%20and%20human%20rights%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20LGBTQIA%2B%20population.%20So%20far%2C%20Humsafar%20has%20extended%20support%20to%20over%201%20lakh%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EContact%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhumsafar.org%2Fcontact-us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4)%20Naz%20Foundation%20(India)%20Trust%2C%20Delhi%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%201994%20by%20Anjali%20Gopalan%2C%20Naz%20Foundation%20has%20been%20a%20pioneer%20in%20advancing%20LGBTQIA%2B%20rights%20in%20India%2C%20including%20leading%20the%202009%20legal%20battle%20that%20first%20struck%20down%20Section%20377.%20Alongside%20legal%20advocacy%2C%20it%20provides%20counselling%2C%20peer%20support%20groups%2C%20medical%20and%20legal%20referrals%2C%20and%20home-based%20care%20for%20people%20living%20with%20HIV%2FAIDS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20LGBTQIA%2B%20initiative%20has%20provided%20face%E2%80%91to%E2%80%91face%20and%20tele%E2%80%91counselling%2C%20medical%20referrals%2C%20home%E2%80%91based%20care%20for%20families%2C%20and%20outreach%20on%20safe%E2%80%91sex%2C%20stigma%20and%20coming%E2%80%91out%20%E2%80%94%20reaching%20over%20234%2C000%20individuals%20to%20date%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20youth-focused%20sports%20programmes%2C%20vocational%20training%2C%20and%20peer%20education%20initiatives%20help%20build%20confidence%20and%20create%20safe%20spaces%20for%20LGBTQIA%2B%20individuals%20across%20the%20country.%20A%20nationwide%20helpline%20(%2B91%208800329176%20%2F%20%2B91%20(011)%2047504630)%20further%20extends%20emotional%20and%20mental%20health%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EContact%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nazindia.org%2Fcontact%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FShanthi-1-1700487723-1749737637.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FShanthi-1-1700487723-1749737637.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FShanthi-1-1700487723-1749737637-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FShanthi-1-1700487723-1749737637-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FShanthi-1-1700487723-1749737637-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuplo